\c 5
\s Inzalo kaAdamu
\p
\v 1 Lolu lugwalo lwezizukulwana zikaAdamu. Mhla uNkulunkulu edala umuntu, wamenza ngokomfanekiso kaNkulunkulu\x + 1.26,27.\x*.
\v 2 Wabadala owesilisa lowesifazana, wasebabusisa, wasebiza ibizo labo \add wathi\add* ngabantu, mhla bedalwa.
\p
\v 3 UAdamu wasephila iminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi amathathu; wasezala \add indodana\add* efuzweni lwakhe njengokomfanekiso wakhe, wabiza ibizo layo \add wathi\add* nguSeti\x + 4.25.\x*.
\v 4 Lensuku zikaAdamu esezele uSeti zaba yiminyaka engamakhulu ayisificaminwembili\x + 1 Lan. 1.1-4. Luka 3.36-38.\x*; wasezala amadodana lamadodakazi.
\v 5 Zonke-ke insuku zikaAdamu, aziphilayo, zaba yiminyaka engamakhulu ayisificamunwemunye lamatshumi amathathu, wasesifa\x + 3.19.\x*.
\p
\v 6 USeti wasephila iminyaka elikhulu lanhlanu; wazala uEnosi\x + 4.26.\x*.
\v 7 USeti wasephila esezele uEnosi iminyaka engamakhulu ayisificaminwembili lesikhombisa; wazala amadodana lamadodakazi.
\v 8 Zonke-ke insuku zikaSeti zaziyiminyaka engamakhulu ayisificamunwemunye letshumi lambili; wasesifa.
\p
\v 9 UEnosi wasephila iminyaka engamatshumi ayisificamunwemunye, wazala uKenani.
\v 10 UEnosi wasephila, esezele uKenani, iminyaka engamakhulu ayisificaminwembili letshumi lanhlanu; wazala amadodana lamadodakazi.
\v 11 Zonke-ke insuku zikaEnosi zaziyiminyaka engamakhulu ayisificamunwemunye lanhlanu; wasesifa.
\p
\v 12 UKenani wasephila iminyaka engamatshumi ayisikhombisa, wazala uMahalaleli.
\v 13 UKenani wasephila, esezele uMahalaleli, iminyaka engamakhulu ayisificaminwembili lamatshumi amane; wazala amadodana lamadodakazi.
\v 14 Zonke-ke insuku zikaKenani zaziyiminyaka engamakhulu ayisificamunwemunye letshumi, wasesifa.
\p
\v 15 UMahalaleli wasephila iminyaka engamatshumi ayisithupha lanhlanu, wazala uJaredi\f + \fk uJaredi: \fl Heb. \fq uJeredi.\f*.
\v 16 UMahalaleli wasephila, esezele uJaredi, iminyaka engamakhulu ayisificaminwembili lamatshumi amathathu; wazala amadodana lamadodakazi.
\v 17 Zonke-ke insuku zikaMahalaleli zaziyiminyaka engamakhulu ayisificaminwembili lamatshumi ayisificamunwemunye lanhlanu; wasesifa.
\p
\v 18 UJaredi wasephila iminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi ayisithupha lambili, wazala uEnoki\x + Juda 14.\x*.
\v 19 UJaredi wasephila, esezele uEnoki, iminyaka engamakhulu ayisificaminwembili; wazala amadodana lamadodakazi.
\v 20 Zonke-ke insuku zikaJaredi zaziyiminyaka engamakhulu ayisificamunwemunye lamatshumi ayisithupha lambili; wasesifa.
\p
\v 21 UEnoki wasephila iminyaka engamatshumi ayisithupha lanhlanu, wazala uMethusela.
\v 22 UEnoki wasehamba loNkulunkulu\x + 5.24. 6.9.\x*, esezele uMethusela, iminyaka engamakhulu amathathu; wazala amadodana lamadodakazi.
\v 23 Zonke-ke insuku zikaEnoki zaziyiminyaka engamakhulu amathathu lamatshumi ayisithupha lanhlanu.
\v 24 UEnoki wasehambahamba loNkulunkulu; kasekho, ngoba uNkulunkulu wamthatha\x + Heb. 11.5. 2 Kho. 2.11.\x*.
\p
\v 25 UMethusela wasephila iminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lesikhombisa, wazala uLameki.
\v 26 UMethusela wasephila, esezele uLameki, iminyaka engamakhulu ayisikhombisa lamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lambili; wazala amadodana lamadodakazi.
\v 27 Zonke-ke insuku zikaMethusela zaziyiminyaka engamakhulu ayisificamunwemunye lamatshumi ayisithupha lesificamunwemunye; wasesifa.
\p
\v 28 ULameki wasephila iminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lambili, wazala indodana.
\v 29 Wasebiza ibizo layo \add wathi\add* nguNowa esithi: Lo uzasiduduza ekusebenzeni kwethu lekutshikatshikeni kwezandla zethu\x + 3.16,17.\x*, ngenxa yomhlabathi, ewuqalekisileyo iN\sc KOSI\x + 3.17.\x*\sc*.
\v 30 ULameki wasephila, esezele uNowa, iminyaka engamakhulu amahlanu lamatshumi ayisificamunwemunye lanhlanu; wazala amadodana lamadodakazi.
\v 31 Zonke-ke insuku zikaLameki zaziyiminyaka engamakhulu ayisikhombisa lamatshumi ayisikhombisa lesikhombisa; wasesifa.
\v 32 UNowa waba leminyaka engamakhulu amahlanu, uNowa wasezala uShemu loHamu loJafethi\x + 10.21.\x*.
